1. *Centar* je središte gradske aktivnosti. (The center is the hub of city activity.)
2. Dječiji *centar* je usmjeren ka promociji zdravog načina života. (The children's center is focused on promoting a healthy lifestyle.)
3. Naš *centar* nudi sve vrste usluga. (Our center provides all sorts of services.)
4. *Centri* se održavaju uslugama za javnost. (Centers are maintained through public services.)
5. U *centru* se nalazi mnogo trgovina. (There are many shops in the center.)
6. Naša *centra* se nalaze širom grada. (Our centers are located all over the city.)